msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.25:0.2"
msgid "3. Sabbavagga"
msgstr "3. All"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 25. Abhiññāpariññāpahānasutta → dutiyapahānasuttaṃ (bj) | pahāna 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn35.25:0.3"
msgid "25. Abhiññāpariññāpahānasutta"
msgstr "25. Giving Up by Direct Knowledge and Complete Understanding"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.17"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn35.25:1.1"
msgid "“Sabbaṃ abhiññā pariññā pahānāya vo, bhikkhave, dhammaṃ desessāmi."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, I will teach you the principle for giving up the all by direct "
"knowledge and complete understanding."

msgctxt "sn35.25:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn35.25:1.3"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sabbaṃ abhiññā pariññā pahānāya dhammo?"
msgstr ""
"And what is the principle for giving up the all by direct knowledge and "
"complete understanding?"

msgctxt "sn35.25:1.4"
msgid ""
"Cakkhuṃ, bhikkhave, abhiññā pariññā pahātabbaṃ, rūpā abhiññā pariññā "
"pahātabbā, cakkhuviññāṇaṃ abhiññā pariññā pahātabbaṃ, cakkhusamphasso "
"abhiññā pariññā pahātabbo, yampidaṃ cakkhusamphassapaccayā uppajjati "
"vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi abhiññā pariññā "
"pahātabbaṃ … pe …"
msgstr ""
"The eye should be given up by direct knowledge and complete understanding. "
"Sights should be given up by direct knowledge and complete understanding. "
"Eye consciousness should be given up by direct knowledge and complete "
"understanding. Eye contact should be given up by direct knowledge and "
"complete understanding. The painful, pleasant, or neutral feeling that "
"arises conditioned by eye contact should be given up by direct knowledge and "
"complete understanding. "

msgctxt "sn35.25:1.5"
msgid ""
msgstr "nose …"

msgctxt "sn35.25:1.6"
msgid ""
"jivhā abhiññā pariññā pahātabbā, rasā abhiññā pariññā pahātabbā, "
"jivhāviññāṇaṃ abhiññā pariññā pahātabbaṃ, jivhāsamphasso abhiññā pariññā "
"pahātabbo, yampidaṃ jivhāsamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā "
"dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi abhiññā pariññā pahātabbaṃ."
msgstr "tongue …"

msgctxt "sn35.25:1.7"
msgid "Kāyo abhiññā pariññā pahātabbo …"
msgstr "body …"

msgctxt "sn35.25:1.8"
msgid ""
"mano abhiññā pariññā pahātabbo, dhammā abhiññā pariññā pahātabbā, "
"manoviññāṇaṃ abhiññā pariññā pahātabbaṃ, manosamphasso abhiññā pariññā "
"pahātabbo, yampidaṃ manosamphassapaccayā uppajjati vedayitaṃ sukhaṃ vā "
"dukkhaṃ vā adukkhamasukhaṃ vā tampi abhiññā pariññā pahātabbaṃ."
msgstr ""
"mind should be given up by direct knowledge and complete understanding. "
"Thoughts should be given up by direct knowledge and complete understanding. "
"Mind consciousness should be given up by direct knowledge and complete "
"understanding. Mind contact should be given up by direct knowledge and "
"complete understanding. The painful, pleasant, or neutral feeling that "
"arises conditioned by mind contact should be given up by direct knowledge "
"and complete understanding."

msgctxt "sn35.25:1.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sabbaṃ abhiññā pariññā pahānāya dhammo”ti."
msgstr ""
"This is the principle for giving up the all by direct knowledge and complete "
"understanding.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.25:1.10"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
